terms (Technical background in engineering, computer science, or MIS a plus)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Strong interpersonal communication (verbal and written) and organizational skills.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Self-motivated; entrepreneurial spirit&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working in a fast pac

