&lt;p&gt;The Finance &amp;amp; BizOps team provides the financial insights and strategic guidance to shape Cloudflare&#39;s growth, profitability, and investment strategy. We&#39;re partners who embed across the business — connecting strategy to execution, driving planning and analysis, and collaborating with cross-functional leaders to develop and deliver key priorities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a seasoned, dynamic senior leader to join this team as the dedicated finance partner to the Developer GTM organization, providing the financial clarity and commercial judgment the business needs to succeed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Developer Platform is one of Cloudflare&#39;s fastest-growing businesses, spanning compute, storage, AI inference, media, and a growing ecosystem of developer tools — delivered through both self-serve and enterprise go-to-market motions, all with distinct commercial models, cost structures, and growth levers. This role is for someone who thrives in that complexity: someone who can work independently across ambiguous problems, build the analysis and frameworks needed, and turn them into recommendations business leaders can act on.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll work across functions — inside and outside of finance — to ensure the platform has coherent financial coverage as it scales. You&#39;ll define and build the models, the cadence, and the relationships, using AI-native tooling as a force multiplier on speed, rigor, and insight — becoming the first call when the business is thinking through a deal, a bet, or a difficult tradeoff. This role reports to the VP of Finance &amp;amp; BizOps.&lt;/p&gt;
